      <h2 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--padding gem-c-heading--margin-bottom-2  ">What Academy for Social Justice does</h2>

    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="grid-row">
    <div class="column-two-thirds">
      
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak " data-module="govspeak">
    
          <p></p>
<div class="govspeak">
<p>The Academy for Social Justice is a networked community of people</p>

<p>Academy for Social Justice works with the <a class="brand__color" href="/government/organisations/ministry-of-justice">Ministry of Justice</a>.</p>
</div>

          <p>
            <a href="/government/organisations/academy-for-social-justice/about" class="brand__color">
              Read more about what we do
            </a>
          </p>

</div>
